OL,3,C'Major incident' declared after bus
OL,4,Ccrash in Camarthenshire
OL,6,FPolice have declared a major incident
OL,7,Fafter a bus was involved in a crash
OL,8,Fnear Kidwelly.
OL,10,FDyfed Powys Police said they are
OL,11,Fdealing with the incident following a
OL,12,Freport of a collision involving a bus
OL,13,Fon the A484.
OL,15,FThe road is closed between the
OL,16,FKidwelly roundabout at Parc y Bocs and
OL,17,FLlandyfaelog, and motorists are asked
OL,18,Fto find alternative routes.
